caption: Lauren (@soitsren) and Donovan's (@jacariisrael) Raleigh apartment has become a colorful, creative oasis with several murals and DIY projects. “For the design, we asked ourselves, ‘How would 13-year-old Lauren and Donovan want to feel when stepping into this space?’” Lauren says. “The result is a space that reflects that playful spirit while giving us room to dream, create, and be our most authentic selves!” See more of this home at the link in our bio ✨
